-- Socar Interested in Petroplus’s Swiss Refinery, RSR Reports
-- B y   S i m e o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2012-01-17T10:50:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-17/socar-interested-in-petroplus-s-swiss-refinery-rsr-reports.html
Socar Trading Co. expressed an
interest in Petroplus Holdings AG’s Swiss oil refinery in
Cressier, RSR radio  reported , citing Thierry Grosjean, the head
of economy in Neuchatel, the canton where the plant is based.  Socar Trading is a unit of State Oil Co. of  Azerbaijan , the
national energy company. Grosjean wasn’t immediately available
for comment and a call to Socar Trading in Geneva wasn’t
returned.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simeon Bennett in Geneva at 
 sbennett9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  